Package: libpacific-mpi0
Section: libs
Architecture: all
Depends: libpacific-mac0-mpi (= ${binary:Version}), libpacific-fluid0-mpi (= ${binary:Version}), libpacific-grains0-mpi (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: PacIFiC MPI runtime libraries (meta-package)
 Convenience package that pulls in all PacIFiC runtime shared libraries built with the distro default MPI.

Package: libpacific-mpi-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: all
Depends:
 libpacific-mac-mpi-dev (= ${binary:Version}), libpacific-fluid-mpi-dev (= ${binary:Version}), libpacific-grains-mpi-dev (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: PacIFiC MPI development files (meta-package)
 Convenience package that pulls in all PacIFiC development components (headers + CMake package files) for the default MPI build.